！"},{"pid":"3391f388bbfac50631eee04749f67a68380da18c","tid":636814,"uid":50088,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T10:45:39.000Z","msg":"其實一定係老毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係因為老毛勁/好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而係孫中山基本上係一個吉祥物而唔係領袖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老孫係就死聯俄容共建國軍之前對佢絕對忠誠既軍隊唔多過一萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基本上除左資歷外係無政治實力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連陳炯明得個福建都話趕佢走就趕佢走就知咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"339d61fd5df92da76c053859afd90cb36f3da65c","tid":636814,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db36676fa6d58f413ffd2fa97b52ccbf2a62ad33","tid":636814,"uid":35790,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"85410fd75757e3160f6240fb2bd112068b2d5925","tid":636814,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T10:33:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T10:39:07.000Z","msg":"孫中山聯俄聯共<br />\n將俄共體制引入中國<br />\n孫中山不愧係新中國國父<br />\n當然比毛對中國影響深遠<br />\n特別係廣東人多得佢唔少"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T11:17:30.000Z","msg":"孫去世時<br />\n廣東人反對孫國葬"},{"pid":"757d24d489911fa51cf56473dbc08ebeb928a76e","tid":636814,"uid":40478,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T11:31:37.000Z","msg":"孫狗炮擊西關父老<br />\n根本係恐怖分子"},{"pid":"f705bb6ce0cc25aac2fe145eb56485f84fdee9f6","tid":636814,"uid":27458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"757d24d489911fa51cf56473dbc08ebeb928a76e","tid":636814,"uid":40478,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T11:31:37.000Z","msg":"孫狗炮擊西關父老<br />\n根本係恐怖分子"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T14:50:45.000Z",